OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FEx-radio host Bolton: BBC  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fspooked over young audience
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Broadcaster Roger Bolton has suggested 
OL,6, the BBC is "spooked" by the decline in 
OL,7, young audiences to traditional radio.  
OL,9,FBolton, 76, was speaking after being   
OL,10,Fdropped as host of Radio 4's Feedback  
OL,11,Fafter 23 years.                        
OL,13,F"If you were running Radio 4, you must 
OL,14,Fbe worried by the fact that not many   
OL,15,Fyoung people are coming to listen to   
OL,16,Fyou," Bolton said.                     
OL,18,FA BBC spokesperson said the station had
OL,19,Falways "kept up with the fast changing 
OL,20,Fbroadcasting landscape".               
